text: The Green Party of Aotearoa New Zealand (), commonly known as the Greens, is a green and left-wing political party in New Zealand. They support ecological wisdom, social justice, grassroots democracy, and nonviolence. The party's ideology are environmentalism with left-wing and social-democratic economic policies. ==References== == Other websites == * Official website Category:1990s establishments in New Zealand Category:1990 establishments in Oceania Category:Green Party of Aotearoa New Zealand
